There is nothing much to read here yet ! Two important points are though available here:
* this binding is in no way usable at this stage. I don't even provide a makefile, this is just an "initial commit" version !!!
* if you want to know what this is about, you must read the D-Bus specification <http://dbus.freedesktop.org/doc/dbus-specification.html>
and also the D-Bus API <http://dbus.freedesktop.org/doc/dbus/api/html/index.html>

